# Engineering (Book 03)

**Constitution:** identify Foundation chapter → state compliance → then code (`docs/foundation/CONSTITUTION.md`).

Full standard: `docs/foundation/03-engineering-standards/12-code-review-and-dod.md`

## Before merge

- `pnpm typecheck` and `pnpm lint` pass
- No secrets in client code; `@nertura/ai` server-only
- DB changes: new migration in `supabase/migrations/`, RLS reviewed
- API routes: Zod validation, consistent error shapes, auth checked

## Patterns

- Match surrounding code; minimal diff; no drive-by refactors
- Copy/i18n: use copy maps (`farm-map-copy.ts` pattern) — not hardcoded English in TR flows
- Map UI: ~73% map / ~27% panel; panel scrolls independently (Book 02, Ch. 08)
- After `pnpm build` while dev was running: `pnpm dev:fresh` — stale `.next` breaks CSS

## Errors

- User-facing: `friendlyDoctorError` / localized copy — not raw provider or stack messages
- Log technical detail server-side only
